15: Taking a stroll through a forest, heh.
20: We aren't in a forest though.
24:
I'm talking about this new VR tech. It
stimulates the five senses—
26:
Sight, sound, smell, touch, and taste.
It's the most realistic forest
experience I've had yet!
29:
Scratch that—this is the best VR
experience I've had, period!
32:
Want to have a go? Just dish up half
the credits I paid for this thing, and
you'll see what I mean.
39: Why not just visit an actual forest?
48:
Incredible... Absolutely stunning! It's
a REAL LIFE FOREST!
52:
The air! The sounds! The visual
effects! Everything's so realistic!
63:
Wait, I should be recording this!
Need to turn the resolution all the
way up... Shoot, my memory storage!
65:
Ahhh, whatever! I'll just use what I
have!
69:
Ahahaha! Yes, yes! Nothing beats
the real deal!
82:
We're in a forest. Of course there's
gonna be bugs.
86:
Hey, this isn't my natural habitat. So
sue me for not knowing it's hot, hard
to traverse, and lacking vending
machines.
88:
Speaking of which, how are you
supposed to find a drink around
here?
93: Lap it up from that spring.
97:
Huh... You sure this is safe to drink?
Has anybody tested this water
before?
100:
Don't worry about it. It's fine...
probably.
105:
How reassuring. Maybe mushrooms
will start growing out of my mouth if—
110:
Guess your zombification will have
to wait.
135:
You SURE nothing weird was in that
water?
151: The night sky. Beautiful, isn't it?
155:
THIS is what nights away from the
city look like? No way...
156:
Who knew a sight like this could
exist...
165:
Did you see it? That was a shooting
star!
169: Do you like the forest now?
177: First you're yes then you're no...
184:
I should sell this data as VR
material... Can you imagine how
much we'd make?
186:
No one owns this forest, right? I can
record whatever without permission?
195:
Oh, I should take a few of these with
me too!
203:
Stimulating the five senses with VR is
great and all, but it's missing an
element of realness.
206:
That's why I'm throwing in this space
stone as a bonus!
211:
Are you talking about that ROCK you
just picked up?! That's fraud, you jerk!
216:
I mean, this IS a stone from another
planet. So TECHNICALLY, that makes
it a space stone.
219:
Hehehe... I'm going to make bank off
this, I just know it!
221:
Forest strolls are just the best! I'm
definitely coming again sometime!
